# 🎤 PM User Interview Skill
### *Generate a User Persona & Simulate a Discovery Interview*

> **Compatible with any AI assistant** — ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Microsoft Copilot, or any LLM chat interface.
> Copy this entire file and paste it as your system prompt or first message.

---

## ▋ WHAT THIS DOES

This prompt turns any AI into a **PM interview simulator**. It will:

1. **Build** a rich, realistic user persona from your three inputs
2. **Become** that user so you can practice live discovery interviews
3. **Answer** your questions the way a real human would — imperfect, specific, and honest

Use it to validate assumptions, explore jobs-to-be-done, or practice before real user sessions.

---

## ▋ HOW TO USE

Fill in the three placeholders below, then paste this entire document into your AI of choice.

```
<User>                    → Who is this person? (role, title, or archetype)
<What does the user do>   → Their job, industry, and core responsibility
<User activity: Primary>  → The ONE workflow or task you want to explore
```

**Example:**
```
<User>                    → Mid-level procurement manager
<What does the user do>   → Approves vendor contracts at a mid-size logistics firm
<User activity: Primary>  → Reviewing and comparing supplier bids
```

