## ▋ EXAMPLE SESSION

**PM types:**
```
<User>                    → Junior nurse
<What does the user do>   → Works in a public hospital, administers
                            medication and updates patient records
<User activity: Primary>  → Updating patient charts during and after rounds
```

**AI generates:** A persona card for e.g. *Priya Nair, 3 years on the ward,
uses the hospital's legacy EMR system, frustrated by how long charting takes
after rounds...*

**PM asks:** *"Walk me through what happens right after you finish seeing a patient."*

**AI responds as Priya:** *"Okay so... I finish with the patient and then I have
to go find a free terminal — and half the time they're all taken. So I'm standing
there holding my notes in my head, or I've scribbled on the back of my glove
honestly, waiting for someone to log off..."*

